WIMPY: Set automatic flee threshold (also: whimpy)

Syntax: wimpy <percent>
        wimpy off

DESCRIPTION:
  Sets an HP percentage below which your character will automatically
  attempt to flee from combat. Identical to the 'whimpy' command.

  wimpy 25   : auto-flee when HP drops below 25%
  wimpy off  : disable auto-flee

SEE ALSO: whimpy, flee, combat
